# Stats & Health — REST Client test file
@baseUrl    = http://localhost:4000
@userToken  = USER_JWT_TOKEN_HERE
@creatorToken = CREATOR_JWT_TOKEN_HERE

### ── HEALTH CHECK (no auth, shows DB + Redis + queue + cron status) ────────────
GET {{baseUrl}}/health

###

### ── DASHBOARD STATS (user) ─────────────────────────────────────────────────────
GET {{baseUrl}}/api/stats/dashboard
Authorization: Bearer {{userToken}}

###

### ── DASHBOARD STATS (creator — more agents + listings) ────────────────────────
GET {{baseUrl}}/api/stats/dashboard
Authorization: Bearer {{creatorToken}}

###

### ── QUEUE STATS (agent + workflow queues) ──────────────────────────────────────
GET {{baseUrl}}/api/agents/queue/stats
Authorization: Bearer {{userToken}}

###
